The best part about this is as there are different flavor flappies. It already scales in power.<br>
<br>
Would that make us as wanted as the holy Trinity?  Nope, not at all and so what?  Im not wanting to break into the holy 3, Im wanting a simple improvement, rather than being a one trick DPS pony.  And please, let the arrogent among us chill out with the &quot;We bring more than... blah blah blah&quot;, I know how to play my class... you know what I mean for heavens sake, chill.<br>
<br>
Its not much, its small, but it could affect that &quot;perception&quot; everyone speaks of so fondly.  You know the perception that we really only bring DPS to a group, and since others bring enough to do the job in a a group AND they heal/summon/buff etc etc...  Yup, its a perception all right.. unfortunately for the sub uber among us more battle tested wizards, its a perception thats accurate. In other words: Its a perception because people are perceptive.<br>
<br>
Bring on &quot;group friendly&quot; flappy, and the perception is gone regardless of where you stand on that.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
