<br>
It isn't that situational to have non-traditional groups.  Most everything outside of PoP (at least in the 51 &amp; under levels) doesn't hit near as hard, or as fast, as PoP mobs.  However, in both groups last night, I had a hard time convincing the bard, then the ranger, that we didn't need a tank or a healer.  Maybe it's because some people don't solo much, so they're not comfortable being able to handle things themselves.  Wizards are.  If it's dk blue, we know we can solo it (unless it summons or something like that).  So, we are less concerned about taking a non-traditional group, and doing something.<br>
<br>
